ActCustoms Act
SubjectRegulations Amending Certain Regulations Made Under the Customs Act (CEFTA, CPFTA and CCOFTA)
PrecisRegulations Amending CERTAIN REGULATIONS MADE UNDER THE CUSTOMS ACT (CEFTA, CPFTA AND CCOFTA) in order to incorporate the Canada-European Free Trade Association Free Trade Agreement, the Canada-Peru Free Trade Agreement and the Canada-Colombia Free Trade Agreement into Canada's existing regulatory framework by allowing customs procedures related to rules of origin to be administered in accordance with the terms of each of these Free Trade Agreements.
